:: Mating-Press-Dialogue [nobr]

<<set _top = $sex.Top || $mc>>
<<set _bottom = $sex.Bottom || _n>>
<<set _spot = $room.location || "floor">>

<<if $sex.role == "Top">>

    You're on top of <<gram _bottom 'subj'>> on the $room.location, $proset.their legs pushed back towards $proset.their head

<<elseif $sex.role == "Bottom">>
    You're on your back $room.location with <<gram _top 'subj'>> on top of you, your legs pushed back towards your head.
<</if>>